@startuml C4_Ecosystem_Marketplace
!include https://raw.githubusercontent.com/plantuml-stdlib/C4-PlantUML/master/C4_Component.puml

title YAWL Ecosystem - Skills & Agents Marketplace

Boundary(marketplace, "Marketplace Platform") {
    Component(listing_mgmt, "ListingManagement", "Catalog", "Publish/discover")
    Component(search_engine, "SearchEngine", "Discovery", "Full-text search")
    Component(rating_system, "RatingSystem", "Trust", "Star ratings")
    Component(payment_processor, "PaymentProcessor", "Commerce", "Billing")
}

Boundary(skill_providers, "Skill Providers") {
    Component(developer, "Developer", "Creator", "Write skills")
    Component(skill_definition, "SkillDefinition", "Package", "Manifest + code")
    Component(version_mgmt, "VersionManagement", "Release", "Semantic versioning")
}

Boundary(skill_catalog, "Skill Catalog") {
    Component(approval_gate, "ApprovalGate", "QA", "Code review + tests")
    Component(published_skill, "PublishedSkill", "Distribution", "Available for use")
    Component(usage_tracking, "UsageTracking", "Analytics", "Download counts")
}

Boundary(skill_consumers, "Skill Consumers") {
    Component(workflow_developer, "WorkflowDeveloper", "User", "Build workflows")
    Component(skill_discovery, "SkillDiscovery", "Browse", "Find + evaluate")
    Component(skill_integration, "SkillIntegration", "Use", "Import into workflow")
}

Boundary(agent_providers, "Autonomous Agent Providers") {
    Component(agent_dev, "Agent Developer", "Creator", "Build agents")
    Component(agent_definition, "AgentDefinition", "Package", "MCP/A2A spec")
    Component(agent_testing, "AgentTesting", "Validation", "Protocol testing")
}

Boundary(agent_catalog, "Agent Catalog") {
    Component(agent_approval, "AgentApproval", "QA", "Protocol validation")
    Component(published_agent, "PublishedAgent", "Distribution", "Available for workflow")
    Component(agent_usage, "AgentUsage", "Analytics", "Usage metrics")
}

developer --> skill_definition: Creates
skill_definition --> approval_gate: Submits
approval_gate --> published_skill: If approved
published_skill --> listing_mgmt: Lists
listing_mgmt --> search_engine: Indexes
workflow_developer --> search_engine: Searches
search_engine --> skill_discovery: Returns
skill_discovery --> skill_integration: Imports
skill_integration --> published_skill: Downloads

agent_dev --> agent_definition: Creates
agent_definition --> agent_testing: Tests
agent_testing --> agent_approval: Submits
agent_approval --> published_agent: If approved
published_agent --> listing_mgmt: Lists

rating_system --> published_skill: Reviews
rating_system --> published_agent: Reviews
payment_processor --> usage_tracking: Tracks revenue

Note as N1
Marketplace Vision:

Skills:
- Reusable task implementations
- Package: code + manifest + tests
- Examples: "SendEmail", "ParseJSON", "CallAPI"
- Version: Semantic versioning (1.0.0)
- Discovery: Search + filter + rate
- Integration: Import into workflow
- Revenue: Developer gets % of usage

Autonomous Agents:
- Workflow-callable agents
- Implements: MCP or A2A protocol
- Examples: "ReviewDocument", "ApproveExpense", "GenerateReport"
- Testing: Protocol compliance
- Discovery: Marketplace listing
- Integration: Invoke as task
- Revenue: Agent provider gets % of calls

Marketplace Features:
1. Listing Management: Publish/unpublish
2. Search Engine: Full-text + filters
3. Rating System: Stars + reviews
4. Payment: Subscription/usage-based
5. Analytics: Usage tracking
6. Quality Gates: Code review, tests, security scan

Trust Signals:
- Author reputation (5 stars, 1000+ downloads)
- Test coverage (≥80%)
- Security scan (no vulnerabilities)
- Community reviews
- Official certification (YAWL Foundation)
End note

SHOW_LEGEND()
@enduml
